: `re.compile(r'<([^:]+)(?::.+)?>')`\r\n\n", "performed_via_github_app": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks/issues/12", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks/issues/12/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks/issues/12/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks/issues/12/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks/issues/12", "id": 377059380, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUzNzcwNTkzODA=", "number": 12, "title": "Tornado extension should use path args, not method args", "user": {"login": "lafrech", "id": 1767010, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE3NjcwMTA=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/1767010?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech", "html_url": "https://github.com/lafrech", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 1081849048, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxMDgxODQ5MDQ4", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks/labels/bug", "name": "bug", "color": "d73a4a", "default": true, "description": "Something isn't working"}, {"id": 1081849051, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxMDgxODQ5MDUx", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks/labels/help%20wanted", "name": "help wanted", "color": "008672", "default": true, "description": "Extra attention is needed"}, {"id": 1119154179, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxMTE5MTU0MTc5", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks/labels/tornado", "name": "tornado", "color": "6066c4", "default": false, "description": "Tornado framework"}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 14, "created_at": "2018-11-03T14:29:45Z", "updated_at": "2020-02-26T16:01:07Z", "closed_at": "2019-12-08T12:40:36Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "<a href=\"https://github.com/zdexter\"><img src=\"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/588935?v=4\" align=\"left\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" hspace=\"10\"></img></a> **Issue by [zdexter](https://github.com/zdexter)**\n_Sunday Oct 08, 2017 at 22:45 GMT_\n_Originally opened as https://github.com/marshmallow-code/apispec/issues/159_\n\n----\n\nCurrently using webargs with `marshmallow` breaks the tornado extension in `apispec`:\r\n\r\n```\r\nfrom webargs.tornadoparser import use_kwargs\r\n\r\nclass MyHandler(RequestHandler):\r\n\r\n    @use_kwargs(SomeMarshmallowSchema())\r\n    def get(self, arg):\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe error is:\r\n```\r\nFile \"spec.py\", line 34, in get\r\nspec.add_path(urlspec=urlspec)\r\nFile \"/usr/local/lib/python3.6/dist-packages/apispec/core.py\", line 191, in add_path\r\nraise APISpecError('Path template is not specified')\r\n```\r\n\r\nthat's because `tornadopath2swagger` gets the method arguments at the python level:\r\n\r\n```\r\n    if sys.version_info >= (3, 3):\r\n        args = list(inspect.signature(method).parameters.keys())[1:]\r\n    else:\r\n        if getattr(method, '__tornado_coroutine__', False):\r\n            method = method.__wrapped__\r\n        args = inspect.getargspec(method).args[1:]\r\n    params = tuple('{{{}}}'.format(arg) for arg in args)\r\n```\r\n\r\nideally `tornadopath2swagger` can call `path_args` and `path_kwargs` on the `RequestHandler` instance (if possible) or otherwise get the path args/kwargs from tornado.\n", "performed_via_github_app": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks/issues/10", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks/issues/10/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks/issues/10/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks/issues/10/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/marshmallow-code/apispec-webframeworks/issues/10", "id": 375244501, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUzNzUyNDQ1MDE=", "number": 10, "title": "Add AUTHORS file", "user": {"login": "lafrech", "id": 1767010, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE3NjcwMTA=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/1767010?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech", "html_url": "https://github.com/lafrech", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/lafrech/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked":